          <p class='first-para'>
            May I just ask the noble Lord one question? Will the Bank be in a position to require this information before the Treasury has made the order referred to in subsection (4)?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0586P0-06029'>
        <a name='S5LV0586P0_19980304_GCR_120'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-mcintosh' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
